{"type":null,"faqId":49533,"title":"更改显示设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"显示设置\"XE \"显示\"XE \"显示屏设置\"XE \"字体设置\"XE \"屏保设置\"XE \"亮度设置\"XE \"休眠设置\"XE \"屏幕旋转\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189880\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“显示”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>在“显示”界面，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“色温”，调整屏幕色温。清除“默认”单选框后，可以手动调节屏幕色温。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“壁纸”，设置锁屏和桌面壁纸。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“字体大小”，设置手机显示的字体大小。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“字体样式”，设置手机显示的字体样式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“互动屏保”，开启或关闭互动屏保功能。开启此功能后，当手机在充电状态下进入休眠时，会自动播放所选屏保图片。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“指示灯”开关，开启或关闭收到通知时指示灯闪烁的功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“显示运营商名称”开关，在非锁屏状态下，状态栏上显示或隐藏运营商名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“显示实时网速”开关，在状态栏上显示或隐藏当前网速。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“亮度”，调整屏幕亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“休眠”，设定屏幕休眠时间。在设定时间内未对手机进行操作，屏幕将自动锁屏以节省电池电量。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“自动旋转屏幕”开关，开启或关闭自动旋转屏幕功能。开启此功能后，当您在浏览网页、查看图片、或编辑信息时旋转手机，屏幕会自动改变显示方向。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5277","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294504000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":102,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}